Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
For the school, it is a good thing because it brings in revenue. On-campus housing is usually more expensive than off-campus ones. Along with the housing, meal plans are made mandatory for those who live on campus. For students it could be good because one would have more oportinities to participate. 